{{DISPLAYTITLE:A_VolcanoBlast}}
'''A_VolcanoBlast'''<br />
(no parameters)

Spawn randomly between 1 and 3 {{Class|VolcanoBlast}} actors 44 units above the calling actor's base. Each of the spawned actors is given a random angle between 0 and 360°, a horizontal velocity along that angle of one unit, and a random vertical velocity between about 2.5 units and 6.5 units. Each spawned actor also plays the sound "world/volcano/shoot" on the BODY channel.

This codepointer is restricted to {{Class|Volcano}} and derived classes.

